    public authHeader() {
        const userLS: any = localStorage.getItem('user');
        const user = JSON.parse(userLS);

        if (user && user.token) {
            return { Authorization: 'Bearer ' + user.token };
        } else {
            return {};
        }
    }

    public getAllCategories() {
        return this.cateogories;
    }

    public getCategories(slug) {
        const requestOptions = { headers: this.headers };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/${slug}`, requestOptions);
    }

    public async getSellerCategories(slug) {
        return await axios.get(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/${slug}`, {
            headers: this.headers,
        });
    }

    public createCategory(category: ICategory, slug: string) {
        const requestOptions = {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: this.headersToken,
            body: JSON.stringify(category),
        };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/${slug}`, requestOptions);
    }

    public updateCategory(category: ICategory, categoryGuid: string) {
        const requestOptions = {
            method: 'PATCH',
            headers: this.headersToken,
            body: JSON.stringify(category),
        };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/detail/${categoryGuid}`, requestOptions);
    }

    public deleteCategory(categoryGuid: string) {
        const requestOptions = {
            method: 'DELETE',
            headers: this.headersToken,
        };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPI()}/catalog/category/detail/${categoryGuid}`, requestOptions);
    }

    public createCategoryVariant(variant: string[], categoryGuid: string) {
        const requestOptions = {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: this.headersToken,
            body: JSON.stringify(variant),
        };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/detail/${categoryGuid}/variant`, requestOptions);
    }

    public updateCategoryVariant(variant: VariantValue[], categoryGuid: string) {
        const requestOptions = {
            method: 'PATCH',

        };
        return fetch(`${environment.setAPIv2()}/catalog/category/detail/${categoryGuid}/variant`, requestOptions);
    }

    public deleteCategoryVariant(variant: VariantValue[], categoryGuid: string) {
